<h3>Step 4: Identify Content Gaps</h3>
<p>Find what competitors are missing.</p>
<p><strong>Common gaps:</strong>
- Outdated statistics
- Missing subtopics
- No visual content
- Poor mobile experience
- Slow page speed
- No FAQ section
- Weak internal linking</p>
